item.title: i rule
item.description: So i was persuing google and i was googling my name - yea know checking up on myself. doing a background search to see if i am insane and worth hanging out with. you know you do.. maybe not on yourself.. but i get concerned that i am too crazy. so i had to check.. anyway.. This is the best thing that has ever happened. Read the article here See my quote.
